summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting an easement over a portion of the southeast one-quarter of Section 2, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; also, portions of Lots 1 and 5, Fern Hill Acre Tracts, and a portion of vacated 37th Avenue Southwest adjoining said Lot 1, for hydrant purposes. (Southwest 107th Street Watermains)
